headline.print_headline: Student Who Subdued Seattle Gunman Says Hero Label Hard to Accept
headline.main: Student Who Subdued Seattle Gunman Says Hero Label Hard to Accept

lead_paragraph: The student who subdued a gunman accused of killing one person and wounding two others at a private Christian college in Seattle said on Monday he found it difficult to accept being hailed as a hero.
